{"tid":2190281,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人自細俾學校貫輸路不拾遺嘅思想，大個先覺得自己ON9？","createTime":"2020-09-05T13:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T14:45:28.000Z","uid":134103,"like":48,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"dbff479fa3dc64a638ab7d5167db0fbee9f7a312","tid":2190281,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺街見到地下有張1000蚊紙，我第一時間其實係想執，但係又即刻覺得呢啲係不義之財，真男人係唔應該貪呢啲小便宜，執唔屬於自己嘅錢好似偷嘢咁，過唔到自己嗰關，所以當睇唔到，就咁行過咗<br />\n<br />\n點知迎頭有個阿叔雙目放光，應該係見到我身後嘅地下嗰張1000蚊，即刻衝鋒21上身，施展惡魔蝙蝠幽靈咁款，一下閃過咗我，執起咗張1000蚊，之後揚長而去<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企之後同屋企人講咗件事，俾佢哋鬧我ON9仔，有錢都唔識執<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗諗下都係，好似我呢啲公屋窮撚，平時返part time交學費做成粒鐘先得嗰幾十蚊，去幫襯黃店想話加三蚊嗌杯凍飲都要左度右度，但係有張1000蚊俾我執竟然都唔執，果然我呢啲垃圾都係要一世做底下階層任人踐踏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />執<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔執"},{"pid":"c45b21a7ff2292a5e14ff3f293382d9cd935cdd5","tid":2190281,"uid":9392,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"作撚完故仔未?"},{"pid":"e172c9c4464f23723e13bfb633210e3378156e0d","tid":2190281,"uid":134103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c45b21a7ff2292a5e14ff3f293382d9cd935cdd5","tid":2190281,"uid":9392,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"作撚完故仔未?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"100%真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱啱發生，新鮮滾熱辣"},{"pid":"b8020efe8ddae0d8a954fca85615b573bf42e78b","tid":2190281,"uid":122709,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202